channel.title: [PI] Couple things with insanity
channel.description:
Thanks for looking guys,
Whenever you leave edge on the wildy on the base im using (project insanity), it teleports you to edge and says: You are not allowed to leave Edgeville or the wilderness.
Im stumped tbh and I wanted to add some minigames and stuff but I cant if it says that every time you leave

item.title: [PI] Couple things with insanity
item.dc:creator: @dragx55 dragx55
item.description:
@dragx55 wrote:

Maybe it’s “player protection”. It’s something I’ve came across when playing a famous private server. It’s basically a measure taken to prevent transferring starters by dieing in the wildy. You have to wait like 1 hour or so for it to wear off.
